{"tid":2118390,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"戰神的鬥志! C朗失戴帽機會後面目猙獰 每分鐘都在拼","createTime":"2020-07-21T12:15:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T17:42:20.000Z","uid":25345,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4827bba79698252db4b24bf3bd17db92da24c1b9","tid":2118390,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:15:10.000Z","msg":"對戰拉素的重磅對決，C朗梅開二度的表現非常搶眼，而且他還打破了諸多紀錄。但是總裁卻並不滿足，他對於進球的饑餓感十足。比賽第63分鐘，迪巴拉主罰左側角球，C朗禁區中路搶到第一點，但是頭球攻門角度太正被門將沒收。C朗對於自己這次丟掉進球機會非常不滿，表情非常沮喪。<br />\n<br />\nC朗沮喪<br />\n<img src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0721/9a945211g00qdsjtu0293c000cw006fc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.ws.126.net%2F2020%2F0721%2F9a945211g00qdsjtu0293c000cw006fc.gif&h=ae8a0e88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n比賽第66分鐘，C朗接到迪巴拉的傳球，禁區內頭球攻門，雖然逃過了門將的封堵，但是卻被橫樑拒之門外。C朗最終也失去了在本場比賽戴帽的機會。"},{"pid":"1721a0a3dc924e21fa3dc436177b1b07d957f429","tid":2118390,"uid":315833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:16:03.000Z","msg":"潛力圖<br />\n<br />\n風化案告唔入個陣可以用"},{"pid":"895d3c2f4784270a0e48814afc70d53de5198fbf","tid":2118390,"uid":37528,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:21:33.000Z","msg":"樣衰都有藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"176a46de5f91b2be7c945149f3d5f24571720c9d","tid":2118390,"uid":90515,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:31:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XG62kyr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXG62kyr.png&h=ecef8343&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7d73c94e3478731fb72af18dddb8b643f8578bc","tid":2118390,"uid":7854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T14:04:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.abc.net.au/news/image/8456442-3x2-940x627.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Fnews%2Fimage%2F8456442-3x2-940x627.jpg&h=b6704ccf&s={SIZE}\" 